Create a Custom Report Type for Approval History

Before creating custom report types, select Report Types from Setup and click New Custom Report Type. Fill out the fields:
Primary Object: Process Instance
Report Type Label: Enter a label (e.g., Approval Process Instances)
Report Type Name: Enter a unique name
Description: Enter a description
Store in Category: Select Administrative Reports

Deployment Status: Deployed
Click Next, select Process Instance Node, and choose an A to B relationship option. Click Save.

After deployment, notify relevant users about the category folder and custom report type to start creating approval history reports.
